WEBVTT

00:15.460 --> 00:19.960
♪During the dark night♪

00:20.100 --> 00:22.750
♪A guiding light♪

00:23.260 --> 00:25.050
♪Just like you♪

00:25.460 --> 00:29.750
♪Makes life turn bright♪

00:30.330 --> 00:35.180
♪Breaking free from darkness♪

00:35.400 --> 00:38.880
♪You gave me strength♪

00:39.230 --> 00:41.780
♪Running for truth♪

00:41.800 --> 00:45.850
♪I find my path♪

00:46.600 --> 00:50.580
♪Drawing on the hope♪

00:51.200 --> 00:54.580
♪That you render me♪

00:55.130 --> 00:58.010
♪In this long journey♪

00:58.260 --> 01:01.680
♪I run on lightly♪

01:19.180 --> 01:22.980
[Reborn]
[Adapted from Qiang Yu's work, Reborn]

01:22.980 --> 01:25.180
[Condition under control]

01:25.180 --> 01:28.890
Qiao Beiyu passed away
on the last Chinese New Year's Eve.

01:29.530 --> 01:32.140
But according to this record,

01:33.220 --> 01:35.300
her condition was stable in December

01:35.490 --> 01:38.250
of the year before.

01:39.330 --> 01:42.979
From stable to gone,

01:42.979 --> 01:45.050
it was less than two months.

01:45.140 --> 01:46.259
That's way too fast.

01:46.810 --> 01:49.140
Do you think

01:49.300 --> 01:50.940
her death wasn't inevitable,

01:51.170 --> 01:52.420
but rather a choice?

01:53.780 --> 01:56.500
What do you mean?

01:56.500 --> 01:58.130
Did Mom and Dad stop the treatment

01:58.130 --> 01:59.130
because they couldn't afford it?

02:00.130 --> 02:00.940
Hey.

02:00.940 --> 02:02.010
That's enough.

02:02.010 --> 02:03.770
Don't forget what you did to Jinrui.

02:03.770 --> 02:05.940
Stop stirring up more trouble.

02:08.930 --> 02:11.350
[Condition under control]

02:46.980 --> 02:50.770
Qiao Beiyu passed away
on the last Chinese New Year's Eve.

02:51.690 --> 02:55.329
From stable to gone,

02:55.329 --> 02:57.490
it was less than two months.

02:57.540 --> 02:58.740
That's way too fast.

02:59.829 --> 03:04.780
[Episode 17]
[Every Family Has Its Troubles]

03:24.490 --> 03:25.930
Mom, it's me.

03:25.930 --> 03:27.020
I'm in Huanzhou.

03:27.260 --> 03:27.690
It's cold.

03:27.690 --> 03:29.410
I brought you and Dad
some thicker clothes.

03:29.820 --> 03:31.780
Qingyu, who told you to come back?

03:31.820 --> 03:33.540
I told you to wait it out
a little longer.

03:33.540 --> 03:34.380
Go back.

03:34.780 --> 03:35.940
I'm in front of the hospital.

03:35.940 --> 03:37.220
I'll leave after giving you the clothes.

03:37.220 --> 03:38.820
It won't take long.

03:39.060 --> 03:40.060
Just go home.

03:40.060 --> 03:41.100
Do not come upstairs.

03:41.170 --> 03:42.220
Just go.

03:43.570 --> 03:44.610
Are you listening?

03:44.660 --> 03:45.450
Mom...

03:47.130 --> 03:47.780
Mom?

04:21.660 --> 04:22.500
Qiao Beiyu!

04:23.500 --> 04:24.380
Qiao Beiyu!

04:38.450 --> 04:39.659
Aren't you sick?

04:39.659 --> 04:41.260
What are you doing here by yourself?

04:43.060 --> 04:45.170
You should put on a jacket. It is cold.

04:45.220 --> 04:47.380
Do you want to get sick again
before getting well?

04:51.940 --> 04:52.820
Do Mom and Dad know

04:52.820 --> 04:54.060
you're standing in the cold?

04:59.060 --> 05:00.730
What is wrong with you?

05:00.730 --> 05:02.060
Mom and Dad haven't come back
to Shunyun for months

05:02.060 --> 05:03.820
because of your treatment.

05:03.940 --> 05:06.170
The shop's closed,
so we're not making any money.

05:06.340 --> 05:08.500
No one bothered to help
when Yu got into trouble at school.

05:08.540 --> 05:10.410
I had to be there
for the parent-teacher meeting.

05:11.220 --> 05:12.540
You're a grown-up.

05:12.540 --> 05:13.570
Be more mature.

05:13.570 --> 05:14.820
We are all worried about you.

05:14.820 --> 05:15.890
Be more considerate.

05:27.890 --> 05:28.690
Qing.

05:30.100 --> 05:32.170
I am a burden to our family,

05:33.380 --> 05:35.220
and our parents.

05:36.690 --> 05:37.780
You're right.

05:41.730 --> 05:43.900
I'll give them back to you, okay?

05:47.780 --> 05:48.580
Not okay.

05:50.340 --> 05:51.780
Not okay at all.

06:09.340 --> 06:10.100
Money!

06:10.580 --> 06:11.900
All you care about is money!

06:13.020 --> 06:15.340
I don't have any money!

06:15.490 --> 06:16.580
Take my life if you will!

06:17.580 --> 06:18.930
I'm not good enough for you?

06:19.540 --> 06:21.730
You were glad
to spend the money I made!

06:22.140 --> 06:23.730
What more do you want from me?

06:23.930 --> 06:24.660
Let go!

06:24.980 --> 06:26.370
Come out!

06:26.370 --> 06:27.020
Let go!

06:27.020 --> 06:28.100
You left me with no choice!

06:28.100 --> 06:28.490
What are you doing?

06:28.490 --> 06:30.410
You're driving me to a dead end!

06:31.660 --> 06:31.980
Come here!

06:31.980 --> 06:32.780
How can I live with this?

06:32.780 --> 06:34.250
We might as well both die now!

06:34.659 --> 06:35.370
Die!

06:35.370 --> 06:36.370
No!

06:36.659 --> 06:36.980
Die!

06:36.980 --> 06:37.700
Help!

06:37.700 --> 06:39.170
Don't hurt my mom!

06:39.170 --> 06:39.980
Let go!

06:40.409 --> 06:47.250
Mumu! Mumu!

06:48.020 --> 06:50.490
Help her up! Quick!

06:50.490 --> 06:50.980
Mumu!

06:50.980 --> 06:52.140
Mumu! I'm sorry!

06:52.140 --> 06:52.900
I'm so sorry!

06:53.370 --> 06:54.780
I'm so sorry, Mumu!

07:06.540 --> 07:07.410
Thanks.

07:09.730 --> 07:10.810
Does your foot still hurt?

07:11.980 --> 07:12.780
Yeah.

07:13.410 --> 07:14.730
It was worth it.

07:15.020 --> 07:16.980
My dad got me injured,

07:17.340 --> 07:18.610
so my mom went all out

07:18.610 --> 07:20.250
to fight him.

07:20.540 --> 07:22.460
My dad actually got intimidated

07:22.460 --> 07:24.250
and promised to quit drinking.

07:26.370 --> 07:29.410
For the first time in a while,
we had breakfast together.

07:29.980 --> 07:32.140
I guess that's the silver lining.

07:32.250 --> 07:33.460
Touch wood.

07:34.290 --> 07:35.020
Mumu.

07:35.900 --> 07:37.580
The disaster relief charity performance
is tomorrow.

07:37.659 --> 07:39.900
Without the lead dancer, what do we do?

07:42.220 --> 07:43.170
Qingyu,

07:43.220 --> 07:45.370
you're good dancer
and you're familiar with the move sets.

07:45.370 --> 07:47.100
Why don't you be our lead dancer?

07:47.460 --> 07:48.250
I'm not cut out for it.

07:48.250 --> 07:49.490
Give it a shot.

07:49.610 --> 07:50.930
The show tomorrow

07:50.930 --> 07:52.700
is the last performance
Mumu and I will do

07:52.700 --> 07:54.220
before we graduate.

07:54.370 --> 07:56.340
It'd be a shame to perform badly.

07:56.340 --> 07:58.170
You wouldn't want Mumu's hard work

07:58.170 --> 07:59.700
to go down the drain, right?

08:04.220 --> 08:04.930
Come on.

08:04.980 --> 08:06.370
Don't pressure Qingyu.

08:15.410 --> 08:17.460
Fine, I get it.

08:17.490 --> 08:18.810
I'm heading out.

08:20.930 --> 08:22.340
Is the shop shorthanded?

08:23.660 --> 08:24.540
Good for you.

08:24.540 --> 08:25.900
You don't have to do a thing.

08:25.930 --> 08:27.850
I only come home twice a week,

08:27.900 --> 08:29.490
and I have to work for free.

08:41.809 --> 08:42.980
Hey, where are my keys?

08:43.460 --> 08:44.580
Check the sofa.

08:45.020 --> 08:46.700
No, I put it in the bag.

08:54.810 --> 08:56.460
Qingyu, did you see my keys?

08:56.460 --> 08:58.540
Move it, or Mom's going to rant again.

09:01.610 --> 09:03.020
I won't lock the door, then.

09:03.370 --> 09:04.490
Stay home and behave.

09:04.490 --> 09:05.290
Do not go out.

09:05.290 --> 09:06.660
Fine. Just go.

09:48.410 --> 09:49.370
Qingyu.

09:49.610 --> 09:51.700
The show tomorrow
is the last performance

09:51.700 --> 09:54.220
Mumu and I will do before we graduate.

09:54.370 --> 09:56.250
You wouldn't want Mumu's hard work

09:56.250 --> 09:57.610
to go down the drain, right?

09:57.610 --> 10:01.730
- Pinky swear. No take-backs.
- Pinky swear. No take-backs.

10:15.530 --> 10:16.490
Come on, Qing.

10:17.220 --> 10:18.420
Raise your arm.

10:19.980 --> 10:21.340
Raise it.

10:26.340 --> 10:28.300
So amazing!

10:30.130 --> 10:31.250
Beiyu.

10:31.250 --> 10:32.340
When can I dance

10:32.340 --> 10:34.820
as well as you?

10:35.340 --> 10:36.650
When you grow up,

10:36.650 --> 10:38.460
you'll be a far greater dancer
than I am.

10:38.490 --> 10:40.980
Okay. Wait until I grow up.

10:40.980 --> 10:41.980
When I'm old enough,

10:41.980 --> 10:43.730
we'll dance together, okay?

10:43.820 --> 10:44.610
Okay!

10:44.890 --> 10:45.130
Come on.

10:45.130 --> 10:45.490
Let's go.

10:45.850 --> 10:49.850
- Pinky swear. No take-backs.
- Pinky swear. No take-backs.

11:30.150 --> 11:34.100
[Disaster Relief Charity Performance
of Binjiang District, Huanzhou City]

11:34.340 --> 11:35.730
Do we have to repeat

11:35.730 --> 11:36.980
the set before the lead solo

11:36.980 --> 11:38.180
since we don't have a lead dancer?

11:38.180 --> 11:39.650
It might be too boring for the audience.

11:39.820 --> 11:40.610
Yeah.

11:40.610 --> 11:41.580
We need the lead dancer

11:41.580 --> 11:43.300
to elevate the mood of the dance.

11:43.490 --> 11:44.250
Without a lead dancer,

11:44.250 --> 11:45.770
the whole performance will be so dull.

11:46.220 --> 11:48.530
Our priority is to finish the show.

11:48.530 --> 11:49.420
The audience

11:49.420 --> 11:50.610
can tolerate a few flaws.

11:50.890 --> 11:52.890
But that would be embarrassing.

11:53.250 --> 11:55.130
Mumu, let's forget it.

11:55.130 --> 11:56.180
We should quit now.

11:56.250 --> 11:57.820
Yeah. Let's forget about it.

11:59.890 --> 12:01.770
Is it too late to join the club?

12:13.890 --> 12:15.650
I thought we were playing basketball.

12:16.180 --> 12:17.770
Why are we watching a show?

12:18.300 --> 12:19.850
It's on the way to the court anyway.

12:20.180 --> 12:21.250
Let's take a break.

12:21.250 --> 12:22.100
Is there a problem?

12:22.490 --> 12:23.420
Nope.

12:23.980 --> 12:24.770
Nope.

12:32.770 --> 12:34.420
A big thanks
to the ladies of Victory Street

12:34.420 --> 12:36.420
for the spectacular performance.

12:36.770 --> 12:38.100
Disasters are cruel, but we are not.

12:38.100 --> 12:38.940
Don't be nervous.

12:39.060 --> 12:40.220
From now on,

12:40.300 --> 12:42.420
you're not the caged bird.

12:42.420 --> 12:43.610
You're soaring in the sky.

12:44.100 --> 12:44.890
Take flight.

12:45.100 --> 12:47.700
Our students are concerned
about world events

12:47.700 --> 12:48.850
and the affected areas.

12:48.940 --> 12:50.600
[Disaster Relief Charity Performance]
Next, let's welcome

12:50.600 --> 12:52.020
[of Binjiang District, Huanzhou]
the dance performance

12:52.020 --> 12:52.700
from Huanzhou High School.

12:52.770 --> 12:54.850
"The Song of Youth."
Let's give them a big round of applause.

12:57.300 --> 12:58.340
So that's why you kept us waiting here.

12:58.340 --> 12:59.370
Can you please keep quiet?

12:59.370 --> 13:00.060
Fine.

13:26.150 --> 13:29.580
♪Under the sunlight♪

13:29.580 --> 13:33.400
♪Birds take a fly♪

13:33.400 --> 13:38.030
♪Raise me up, hold me high♪

13:38.030 --> 13:41.330
♪Only you♪

13:41.900 --> 13:46.380
♪During the dark night♪

13:46.380 --> 13:49.850
♪A guiding light♪

13:49.850 --> 13:51.480
♪Just like you♪

13:51.480 --> 13:56.430
♪Makes life turn bright♪

13:56.430 --> 14:01.540
♪Breaking free from darkness♪

14:01.540 --> 14:06.340
♪You gave me strength♪

14:06.340 --> 14:08.780
♪Running for truth♪

14:08.780 --> 14:13.830
♪I find my path♪

14:13.830 --> 14:18.050
♪Drawing on the hope♪

14:18.050 --> 14:21.650
♪That you render me♪

14:21.650 --> 14:25.000
♪In this long journey♪

14:25.000 --> 14:27.800
♪I run lightly♪

15:22.490 --> 15:23.530
If you turn around,

15:23.890 --> 15:24.980
I'll always be there.

15:51.460 --> 15:52.220
Mom, slow down.

15:52.460 --> 15:53.220
What is over there?

15:54.580 --> 15:59.820
Great!

16:04.700 --> 16:06.220
Is that Qingyu?

16:07.820 --> 16:08.490
Wait...

16:13.010 --> 16:13.980
Qiao Qingyu!

16:15.650 --> 16:16.130
Hey.

16:16.420 --> 16:16.890
What's wrong?

16:16.890 --> 16:18.370
Mumu, my mom is here. What now?

16:18.370 --> 16:19.890
Your mom is here? Oh no.

16:22.940 --> 16:23.890
Did you see Qiao Qingyu?

16:23.890 --> 16:24.850
Madam, what are you doing here?

16:24.850 --> 16:25.700
Did you watch our performance?

16:25.700 --> 16:26.770
Where is Qiao Qingyu?

16:26.770 --> 16:28.770
Qingyu? Why would she be here?

16:29.730 --> 16:30.420
Mumu.

16:30.820 --> 16:32.130
Where is Qingyu?

16:32.820 --> 16:34.420
There's no way she can be here.

16:34.420 --> 16:35.730
You must be mistaken.

16:41.580 --> 16:42.700
Perhaps you're right.

18:28.860 --> 18:29.490
Qingyu.

18:31.290 --> 18:34.570
Was it you on the stage today?

18:37.090 --> 18:38.620
I knew it.

18:39.250 --> 18:40.050
Don't worry.

18:40.220 --> 18:42.380
I managed to convince Mom it wasn't you.

18:43.860 --> 18:44.660
Thanks.

18:50.380 --> 18:51.050
Qingyu.

18:52.530 --> 18:55.810
The dance was pretty nice.

18:56.900 --> 18:58.620
You were as good as Beiyu.

19:34.250 --> 19:35.140
Qingyu.

19:35.420 --> 19:36.250
Sit here.

19:44.810 --> 19:46.010
Just sit down.

19:46.700 --> 19:48.330
Meixi set aside a spot for you.

19:48.330 --> 19:49.810
I didn't. Don't be silly.

19:51.770 --> 19:52.860
There are only three of us.

19:52.860 --> 19:54.460
Let's eat lunch together from now on.

19:54.530 --> 19:56.090
Yeah, we can reserve the spot for you.

19:58.860 --> 19:59.660
Thanks.

20:02.050 --> 20:03.490
Let's put the past behind us.

20:03.980 --> 20:05.090
Do not bring it up again.

20:05.770 --> 20:06.620
Fine. We get it.

20:07.220 --> 20:07.860
Qingyu.

20:07.860 --> 20:08.660
Let's check out

20:08.660 --> 20:10.180
the corner shop later.

20:17.620 --> 20:18.490
Fatty meat.

20:34.330 --> 20:36.330
- "How are you?"
- Very good.

20:36.620 --> 20:38.330
This is the practice exercise

20:38.460 --> 20:39.620
for

20:39.620 --> 20:40.620
the TEF and DELF.

20:40.860 --> 20:42.530
We still have some time left.

20:42.530 --> 20:43.860
You may use the time to see

20:43.860 --> 20:44.700
if there is anything

20:44.700 --> 20:47.570
you don't understand.

20:53.830 --> 20:55.380
[Wu]
Mr. Ming's case

20:55.530 --> 20:56.940
seems to have escalated.

20:57.660 --> 20:59.530
You should check on your dad.

21:01.420 --> 21:04.830
[Notice of Suspension
for Pending Investigation]

21:21.460 --> 21:21.980
Make sure patient on Bed 3

21:21.980 --> 21:24.460
doesn't eat 12 hours before surgery.

21:24.730 --> 21:25.770
And the one on Bed 27...

21:25.770 --> 21:26.490
Yanqiu.

21:27.810 --> 21:29.570
There's something
I'd like to talk about.

21:32.940 --> 21:33.660
Yanqiu.

21:34.730 --> 21:36.660
Is what people say about my dad true?

21:37.290 --> 21:40.140
Did he get someone killed
because of money?

21:46.330 --> 21:49.140
The patient was in the late stage
of his sickness.

21:49.140 --> 21:50.770
It was hilar cholangiocarcinoma.

21:51.570 --> 21:53.180
The risk of surgery was too high.

21:53.290 --> 21:54.220
Before she came,

21:54.220 --> 21:55.460
she was rejected by several hospitals.

21:56.090 --> 21:58.730
The patient and her husband
knelt on the floor

21:59.220 --> 22:00.980
and begged your dad to save her life.

22:01.700 --> 22:03.980
Your dad accepted them
despite the objection.

22:04.810 --> 22:05.860
The surgery was a success,

22:06.330 --> 22:08.010
but complications arose afterward.

22:08.770 --> 22:10.250
To save the patient's life,

22:10.700 --> 22:12.860
your dad gave her a second surgery.

22:15.050 --> 22:15.730
Sadly,

22:16.290 --> 22:17.770
the patient didn't make it.

22:20.460 --> 22:21.090
And then,

22:21.290 --> 22:23.860
the patient's in-laws didn't want
to pay the medical bill,

22:24.330 --> 22:25.980
so they blamed your dad
for unnecessary health care.

22:26.940 --> 22:28.620
The hospital suspended him
for further investigation.

22:35.220 --> 22:36.290
Was it worth it

22:37.050 --> 22:38.180
to have done it?

22:41.420 --> 22:42.220
Save that question

22:42.330 --> 22:43.570
for your dad.

22:45.530 --> 22:46.940
The Ming Qiuxin I know

22:48.090 --> 22:50.940
has always silently done
what he thinks is right

22:50.940 --> 22:52.490
with great determination.

22:53.570 --> 22:56.140
Even if he is misunderstood or wronged,

22:57.050 --> 22:58.730
he won't find excuses for himself.

22:59.220 --> 23:00.420
He's the same at work

23:00.810 --> 23:02.730
and in life.

23:25.250 --> 23:25.900
Sheng?

23:27.250 --> 23:28.090
What are you doing here?

23:29.140 --> 23:29.770
I live here.

23:29.770 --> 23:30.980
Why can't I be here?

23:31.050 --> 23:32.420
Of course you can.

23:33.330 --> 23:34.220
I'm only here

23:34.220 --> 23:35.140
to pick up some stuff.

23:35.660 --> 23:36.050
Oh.

23:38.460 --> 23:39.380
Your food is burned.

23:40.050 --> 23:40.570
Oh.

23:50.920 --> 23:54.510
[A Guide to Studying in France
for Undergraduates]

24:22.860 --> 24:23.980
Since I've got some time

24:24.140 --> 24:25.380
the past few days,

24:26.090 --> 24:27.810
I gathered some info.

24:28.900 --> 24:29.730
Take a look.

24:29.770 --> 24:30.770
If you find it useful,

24:31.290 --> 24:32.090
feel free to take it.

24:40.010 --> 24:41.330
Have you eaten?

24:42.460 --> 24:43.570
Join me.

24:44.530 --> 24:45.900
I learned a few new recipes.

24:45.900 --> 24:46.660
Try my cooking.

24:50.380 --> 24:51.180
Fine.

24:52.420 --> 24:53.980
Great. Wait here.

25:05.250 --> 25:06.420
The shop isn't shorthanded.

25:06.660 --> 25:09.010
Your mom wants you to do your homework,

25:09.010 --> 25:10.620
so I'm here to deliver your meal.

25:13.570 --> 25:14.620
Finish it while it's warm.

25:14.980 --> 25:15.980
What about you?

25:16.090 --> 25:17.010
I've had mine.

25:24.010 --> 25:24.860
Qing.

25:25.010 --> 25:25.530
Hmm?

25:26.380 --> 25:28.530
Have you heard about Jinrui?

25:30.700 --> 25:32.420
People from his workplace heard

25:32.420 --> 25:33.730
about his scandal with Bei.

25:34.050 --> 25:36.620
He quit his job and went missing.

25:36.620 --> 25:38.380
His parents are worried about him.

25:38.380 --> 25:39.380
They've searched everywhere.

25:39.380 --> 25:40.220
So what?

25:40.220 --> 25:41.570
He had it coming.

25:45.250 --> 25:48.010
There's something
your mom wouldn't let me tell you,

25:48.330 --> 25:50.420
but I think you should know.

25:51.570 --> 25:53.530
After you sabotaged Jinrui's wedding,

25:53.660 --> 25:55.180
his parents wasn't going

25:55.180 --> 25:56.490
to let you off.

25:56.570 --> 25:57.460
They were going

25:57.460 --> 25:58.460
to make a scene in your school

25:58.460 --> 25:59.940
so you would have to drop out.

26:00.940 --> 26:01.940
It was Jinrui

26:02.140 --> 26:03.900
who warned them
not to cause you trouble.

26:03.900 --> 26:05.620
Only then did they give up.

26:07.620 --> 26:08.490
Qing.

26:09.570 --> 26:12.530
I do think
Jinrui has made some mistakes,

26:13.570 --> 26:15.730
but he is not an unforgivable villain.

26:28.090 --> 26:28.900
Eat up.

26:49.570 --> 26:52.460
Wang!

26:56.730 --> 26:58.420
Can we go with him as his family?

26:58.700 --> 26:59.420
Is that okay?

26:59.660 --> 27:00.660
Wang!

27:32.660 --> 27:33.900
Is Mumu not here?

27:34.140 --> 27:35.090
She is away

27:35.090 --> 27:37.010
for some family issues.

27:55.420 --> 27:56.090
Mom.

27:59.770 --> 28:01.460
What took you so long to leave school?

28:01.730 --> 28:03.050
Was the class extended again?

28:04.900 --> 28:06.010
Grab a bite.

28:07.860 --> 28:08.660
Well...

28:08.810 --> 28:10.050
Mumu's dad got sick.

28:10.050 --> 28:11.380
I want to visit her.

28:15.690 --> 28:19.100
[Huanzhou People's Hospital]

28:27.380 --> 28:28.530
Cut it out.

28:37.810 --> 28:39.810
Madam, Qingyu, thanks for coming.

28:41.490 --> 28:42.140
Mumu,

28:42.770 --> 28:44.980
we're here to visit your dad.

28:46.180 --> 28:47.290
Have you eaten?

28:48.860 --> 28:49.570
Qingyu,

28:49.570 --> 28:51.330
go grab some food with Mumu.

28:52.250 --> 28:53.050
I'll be right here.

29:02.090 --> 29:03.730
Have some noodles.

29:26.290 --> 29:28.250
My dad has terminal liver cancer.

29:29.570 --> 29:30.490
According to the doctor,

29:31.660 --> 29:32.940
going through chemo

29:33.140 --> 29:34.330
might buy him a few years.

29:35.050 --> 29:36.460
Without the chemo,

29:37.460 --> 29:38.460
he will be gone soon.

29:40.180 --> 29:43.250
When my dad got drunk,

29:44.250 --> 29:45.460
I had wished

29:45.660 --> 29:47.330
for him to die so many times.

29:48.290 --> 29:49.730
But when it's finally happening,

29:52.380 --> 29:54.050
I don't know how to face it.

29:59.770 --> 30:00.620
These days,

30:01.010 --> 30:02.380
he seems like a different person.

30:02.700 --> 30:03.490
He said

30:04.090 --> 30:05.860
he should have
taken better care of himself.

30:07.420 --> 30:08.460
He's not afraid of pain.

30:08.730 --> 30:09.730
He wants the chemo.

30:13.490 --> 30:14.770
But Mom says...

30:17.010 --> 30:18.330
the chemo won't cure him,

30:19.330 --> 30:21.140
and it's too expensive.

30:21.530 --> 30:23.330
We are already deep in debt.

30:25.570 --> 30:27.530
How can we afford to pay the debts?

30:30.640 --> 30:31.440
Qingyu...

30:36.810 --> 30:38.330
I'm about to lose my dad.

30:54.180 --> 30:55.220
What do I do now?

31:04.220 --> 31:08.380
I visited Mumu's dad at the hospital.

31:09.940 --> 31:11.140
Terminal liver cancer.

31:11.980 --> 31:13.140
He can't even have surgery.

31:13.860 --> 31:15.700
He won't be around for much longer.

31:16.490 --> 31:19.220
What about the chemo?

31:21.220 --> 31:22.980
Each treatment costs over ten grand.

31:24.380 --> 31:25.700
They can't afford it.

31:27.330 --> 31:28.380
When you get this disease,

31:29.180 --> 31:30.090
your fate is sealed.

31:30.940 --> 31:32.660
Spending money is pointless.

31:33.730 --> 31:34.770
Indeed.

31:34.980 --> 31:35.860
In the end,

31:36.860 --> 31:38.530
you lose the money and the person.

31:38.730 --> 31:40.180
The whole family suffers.

31:40.570 --> 31:41.730
How miserable.

31:42.620 --> 31:44.180
If I ever get sick,

31:44.620 --> 31:46.050
don't get me treated.

31:49.460 --> 31:50.570
You'd better not get sick.

31:51.570 --> 31:54.490
Hey, use this for massage
when you have the time.

31:55.980 --> 31:56.860
Come on.

31:57.770 --> 31:58.730
It's good for health.

31:58.770 --> 31:59.290
Forget it.

31:59.290 --> 32:00.730
It takes care of the vital organs.

32:00.730 --> 32:03.180
The spleen, the stomach,

32:03.620 --> 32:05.730
and anything of the sort.

32:06.290 --> 32:07.180
I'm busy.

32:33.790 --> 32:35.850
[Medical dispute mediation]

32:43.190 --> 32:44.170
[How to resolve medical dispute]

33:05.530 --> 33:06.620
You know what?

33:07.050 --> 33:08.570
It's Wang from Block 38.

33:09.770 --> 33:10.570
What is it?

33:10.660 --> 33:11.770
The drunkard.

33:11.770 --> 33:12.420
He is sick.

33:12.810 --> 33:13.490
Liver cancer.

33:13.730 --> 33:14.860
Seriously?

33:14.860 --> 33:15.380
Yeah.

33:15.380 --> 33:18.290
He doesn't look that old.

33:18.660 --> 33:20.250
How did he get sick?

33:20.660 --> 33:21.730
Guess what?

33:22.050 --> 33:24.460
The moment he was diagnosed,

33:24.460 --> 33:26.250
his wife made the statement.

33:26.940 --> 33:28.180
"We're not getting the treatment."

33:28.620 --> 33:29.900
But given the situation,

33:29.900 --> 33:31.460
she can't just leave him to die.

33:31.490 --> 33:33.220
She has her reasons.

33:34.380 --> 33:34.770
Madam.

33:34.770 --> 33:35.330
Welcome.

33:36.140 --> 33:36.490
She's here.

33:36.490 --> 33:38.220
I'll have a bowl of plain noodles
to eat here.

33:38.250 --> 33:39.290
And a bowl of pork chop noodles

33:39.290 --> 33:40.490
to go, please.

33:40.490 --> 33:41.380
Sure thing.

33:41.380 --> 33:41.980
Thanks.

33:41.980 --> 33:43.730
Take a seat.

33:46.090 --> 33:46.980
It's quiet here.

33:47.980 --> 33:48.860
I'll be right back.

33:51.140 --> 33:52.460
Plain noodles and pork chop noodles.

34:00.900 --> 34:02.050
Plain noodles.

34:03.380 --> 34:03.860
Here you go.

34:03.860 --> 34:04.460
Thanks.

34:04.570 --> 34:05.490
And the pork chop noodles.

34:06.660 --> 34:07.620
I didn't order the meat.

34:07.620 --> 34:08.699
Eat up. It's okay.

34:12.810 --> 34:13.980
Take care of yourself.

34:41.469 --> 34:45.580
[Outpatient Department]

34:45.580 --> 34:54.179
[Join Us
for the Red Ribbon Campus Tour.]

34:54.179 --> 34:54.980
Miss,

34:55.050 --> 34:56.219
let me give you a hand.

35:00.250 --> 35:01.330
Red Ribbon?

35:03.570 --> 35:04.570
Ms. Le Fan.

35:04.770 --> 35:06.050
Are you a volunteer?

35:07.220 --> 35:07.810
Yeah.

35:08.010 --> 35:09.090
I provide counseling

35:09.090 --> 35:10.460
to those who need it,

35:10.460 --> 35:12.860
helping them integrate
into families and society.

35:12.860 --> 35:15.010
Are you interested?

35:17.940 --> 35:18.730
How about this?

35:19.420 --> 35:21.570
We have volunteer activities
every Saturday.

35:21.570 --> 35:22.570
You are welcome to join.

35:23.370 --> 35:26.100
[Huanzhou Association of AIDS Prevention
and Control]

35:28.010 --> 35:29.290
Have you seen Wang Mumu?

35:29.530 --> 35:30.290
Wang Mumu!

35:31.090 --> 35:32.010
What is it, miss?

35:32.130 --> 35:34.460
Your aunt just called.
She wants you at the hospital.

35:40.940 --> 35:42.340
You know how difficult things are

35:42.340 --> 35:43.740
for this family.

35:44.740 --> 35:46.260
There's nothing I can do.

35:47.690 --> 35:48.650
We know

35:48.650 --> 35:50.340
you are in a tough situation.

35:50.340 --> 35:51.490
We discussed the matter

35:51.490 --> 35:53.010
on our way here.

35:53.010 --> 35:55.050
We will lend you

35:55.170 --> 35:56.820
the money you need

35:56.860 --> 35:57.980
for the treatment.

35:58.260 --> 36:00.570
Mumu's great grades

36:00.610 --> 36:01.900
are setting her up
for an amazing future.

36:02.340 --> 36:02.940
No.

36:03.780 --> 36:04.940
Mumu is just a girl.

36:05.380 --> 36:07.050
You're making her carry her dad's debts.

36:07.170 --> 36:07.980
I won't agree with this.

36:07.980 --> 36:09.460
Nothing works for you!

36:09.460 --> 36:11.010
What is it that you want?

36:11.260 --> 36:13.260
Do you want my son to die?

36:13.300 --> 36:15.420
We are here to solve the problem.

36:15.420 --> 36:16.260
We are a family.

36:16.260 --> 36:18.050
I won't drag Mumu into this.

36:18.900 --> 36:20.690
We are not getting the treatment.

36:21.130 --> 36:22.780
If your son doesn't make it through,

36:22.780 --> 36:23.780
you can come after me.

36:23.980 --> 36:25.980
You heartless wretch!

36:26.300 --> 36:27.780
What's wrong with you?

36:29.490 --> 36:30.130
You've lost your mind!

36:30.340 --> 36:31.340
Stop it!

36:33.530 --> 36:34.420
You're in a hospital.

36:34.610 --> 36:35.610
Fight somewhere else.

36:37.260 --> 36:38.900
Sorry. We'll keep quiet.

36:39.090 --> 36:40.130
It's all right.

36:40.940 --> 36:42.530
We are here to solve the problem.

36:52.490 --> 36:53.170
Mumu.

36:55.340 --> 36:58.740
I've been thinking about the past.

37:01.090 --> 37:02.260
You were still little.

37:03.570 --> 37:05.490
Every year
at the Chinese Lantern Festival,

37:06.210 --> 37:07.820
you, me,

37:08.610 --> 37:09.690
and your mom

37:10.820 --> 37:13.780
would go to the lantern fair together.

37:15.940 --> 37:17.610
You were always a smart kid.

37:19.340 --> 37:20.940
You'd say you were tired after a while.

37:21.980 --> 37:22.940
You reached out

37:23.380 --> 37:24.530
and grabbed me,

37:24.820 --> 37:26.050
wanting me to carry you

37:26.740 --> 37:28.340
so you could ride on my shoulders.

37:33.170 --> 37:33.980
Back then,

37:35.300 --> 37:37.610
we were a happy family

37:38.380 --> 37:39.650
and had a great time.

37:41.130 --> 37:42.210
Do you remember that?

37:45.780 --> 37:46.650
I do.

37:48.650 --> 37:49.460
I know

37:51.210 --> 37:53.210
I've made too many mistakes
over the years.

37:54.860 --> 37:56.050
I've let you

37:57.050 --> 37:58.210
and your mom down.

38:00.010 --> 38:01.050
I deserve

38:03.260 --> 38:04.460
to get sick.

38:09.090 --> 38:11.050
But I am dying.

38:16.260 --> 38:17.690
I don't want to leave you.

38:20.340 --> 38:21.050
Mumu.

38:23.530 --> 38:25.820
I want to see you go to college,

38:27.780 --> 38:29.210
get your first job,

38:30.420 --> 38:32.420
get married, and start a family.

38:43.530 --> 38:45.460
We can't afford the treatment.

38:47.380 --> 38:49.820
I can't trouble you
and your mom anymore.

38:49.900 --> 38:51.940
Mumu, I'm sorry for everything.

38:52.820 --> 38:54.530
I was so wrong.

38:54.740 --> 38:55.460
If...

38:55.460 --> 38:57.300
If I could get another chance,

38:57.300 --> 38:59.650
I'd treat you and your mom well.

39:00.090 --> 39:00.820
Okay?

39:01.610 --> 39:02.420
Mumu...

39:06.340 --> 39:07.130
Mumu...

39:57.380 --> 39:57.940
Here you are.

39:58.170 --> 39:59.010
Thank you.

40:01.860 --> 40:03.690
Do you know that family?

40:04.740 --> 40:08.260
Oh. They've been my neighbors
my entire life.

40:08.460 --> 40:09.940
They live across Grandpa's place.

40:13.300 --> 40:15.740
Was it the same
with the patient who begged my dad

40:17.130 --> 40:18.010
to treat her?

40:25.780 --> 40:27.780
When a person's life reaches the end,

40:29.260 --> 40:30.380
their fate

40:30.380 --> 40:32.490
is in the hands
of their family and doctors.

40:34.170 --> 40:36.340
Hope or despair, it's all determined

40:37.300 --> 40:39.210
by either one of them.

40:41.420 --> 40:42.210
By the way,

40:42.740 --> 40:44.460
the mediation panel decided on a time.

40:44.530 --> 40:45.890
The investigation
of your dad's medical dispute

40:45.900 --> 40:46.980
is next week.

40:47.380 --> 40:47.980
Okay.

40:49.420 --> 40:52.210
Yanqiu,
could you look something up for me?

40:53.380 --> 40:54.570
After Tan Qianqian's passing,

40:54.570 --> 40:56.130
her husband never showed up again.

40:56.170 --> 40:56.690
He won't answer

40:56.690 --> 40:57.300
our phone calls.

40:57.820 --> 40:59.650
But her great-aunt came
and caused some trouble a few times.

41:00.260 --> 41:01.740
They refuse to pay the medical bill

41:01.740 --> 41:03.090
while asking for compensation.

41:03.740 --> 41:05.170
Your dad's medical dispute mediation

41:05.300 --> 41:06.490
was their request.

41:07.260 --> 41:08.490
Did you try searching

41:08.490 --> 41:09.610
for Tan Qianqian's husband?

41:09.610 --> 41:10.210
We did,

41:10.210 --> 41:11.380
but to no avail.

41:12.610 --> 41:13.490
There's something

41:14.420 --> 41:15.650
that was quite peculiar.

41:16.780 --> 41:18.900
Our department received a pack of cash.

41:18.980 --> 41:21.300
It was designated
as payment for Tan Qianqian's bill.

41:21.900 --> 41:23.170
Yet we don't know who sent it.

41:58.880 --> 42:02.570
♪Perhaps♪

42:03.080 --> 42:08.780
♪The more we care,
the more careful we become♪

42:09.920 --> 42:15.320
♪Counting the distance
that separates us♪

42:16.320 --> 42:21.880
♪A single step,
and we'd be closer still♪

42:27.550 --> 42:31.220
♪In the future♪

42:31.680 --> 42:37.400
♪Time will reveal this secret♪

42:38.900 --> 42:43.970
♪Waiting is a silent promise♪

42:45.220 --> 42:50.380
♪That never expires♪

42:53.980 --> 42:58.450
♪Turns out that what's on my mind♪

42:59.450 --> 43:03.120
♪Is your name♪

43:03.620 --> 43:08.720
♪The only stubbornness in my heart♪

43:09.800 --> 43:13.020
♪At first sight♪

43:13.450 --> 43:16.730
♪The future has been determined♪

43:17.420 --> 43:22.980
♪Dreams began to feel real♪

43:24.080 --> 43:27.620
♪Turns out that what's on your mind♪

43:28.080 --> 43:32.020
♪Is a place♪

43:32.320 --> 43:37.880
♪Where the same story is held dear♪

43:38.550 --> 43:41.920
♪Fortunately, I'm not sensible enough♪

43:42.250 --> 43:45.720
♪Courage wasn't late too♪

43:46.250 --> 43:52.320
♪Only then does time not betray
our acquaintance♪
